OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy with most parts dry,
OL,6,Fbut also a few showers, perhaps heavy.
OL,7,FWarm in any brighter spells that
OL,8,Fdevelop. Heavy rain and gusty winds
OL,9,Fthen move east late afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FSunny
OL,12,Fspells and showers Thursday. Cloud
OL,13,Fthickening overnight, with some rain.
OL,14,FCloudy Friday, before heavy rain band
OL,15,Fspreads east later. Sunny spells and
OL,16,Fshowers Saturday. Warm in any brighter
OL,17,Fspells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
